snippet.title: Combo Card Clashers - Dev Log #3: The Journey
snippet.description:
Hey everyone, with the upcoming release of the prologue on 1/17/2024, I wanted to share my journey for this games development in a quick video. 

If you enjoyed the video, please Wishlist the prologue here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2668680/Combo_Card_Clashers_Prologue/

Also, you can wishlist the main game here:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2054770/Combo_Card_Clashers/

Thanks for watching!
